spx.packets

Class AVInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.AVInfo

  • public class AVInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for holding an AVInfo packet received from the network.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ structure SPxPacketAVInfo from "SPxPackets.h".
